name: Festa do Rosario
description:
Rosary Feast

A great celebration that takes place in the months of November in Curitiba.

Generally the party is united to November 20th, the date that celebrates the importance of Zumbi dos Palmares.
 
This commemorative day celebrates the culture, customs and Afro-Brazilian religions. 

Curitiba, Brasil.
